data.description: This beautifully fully remodeled home welcomes you with plank flooring and  large open floor plan.  The kitchen features white cabinetry in with black granite countertops and a spectacular eat in black kitchen island with white quartz waterfall countertops.  The large living space exhibits an amazing fireplace accent wall.  The owners quarters has custom  molding on the walls and  a separate tub shower in the bath.  The backyard has an above ground 15 ft swim spa, two raised garden beds and lots of space to relax.  This home features full solar panels to save on energy all year long.
